{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.680", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.960", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.360", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei den Koalitionspartnern ist in den letzten Tagen ganz kurzfristig eine bemerkenswerte Erkenntnis herangereift, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.240", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die da lautet: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.880", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bis zum 30.\u00a0Juni ist es nicht mehr lang hin. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.840", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Also wurde die Verl\u00e4ngerung der Regelung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.160", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wonach der Streitwert einer Nichtzulassungsbeschwerde zum Bundesgerichtshof mindestens 20\u00a0000\u00a0Euro betragen muss, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.040", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "spontan noch auf die Tagesordnung gesetzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.920", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sonst w\u00e4re die Wertgrenze Ende Juni ausgelaufen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.280", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In die entsprechende Drucksache schreibt die Gro\u00dfe Koalition, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.680", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "man wolle mit der Verl\u00e4ngerung erm\u00f6glichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.640", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Entwicklung der Gesch\u00e4ftsbelastung des BGH f\u00fcr einen Zeitraum von anderthalb Jahren zu beobachten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.520", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren von CDU, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.600", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "CSU und SPD, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.920", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Regelung in \u00a7\u00a026 Nr.\u00a08 EGZPO wurde im Zuge der gro\u00dfen ZPO-Reform 2001 als \u00dcbergangsregelung beschlossen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.160", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im EGZPO versteckt und seitdem viermal verl\u00e4ngert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.840", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "immer wieder mit der Begr\u00fcndung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.520", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "man wolle beobachten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.680", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren von CDU, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.400", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "CSU und SPD, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.560", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was Sie \u201ebeobachten\u201c nennen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.280", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nennen wir Freie Demokraten \u201eschlafen\u201c."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.680", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "16\u00a0Jahre des Beobachtens sind genug. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.480", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Entsprechend hatte der Kollege von der SPD bei der letzten Verl\u00e4ngerung der Regelung im Jahr\u00a02016 auch bereits angek\u00fcndigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.800", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Wertgrenze werde ein letztes Mal verl\u00e4ngert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.800", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Redner von SPD und CDU/CSU waren sich einig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.040", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man grunds\u00e4tzlich debattieren muss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.720", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was ist seitdem passiert? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.960", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Offenbar ging es schlicht in GroKo-Manier weiter so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.560", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und heute stehen wir wieder hier."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.960", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.280", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nat\u00fcrlich w\u00e4re es nicht verantwortlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.920", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Regelung jetzt auslaufen zu lassen und den BGH mit einer entsprechend bef\u00fcrchteten Nichtzulassungsbeschwerdeflut lahmzulegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.800", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wir erwarten von den Koalitionsfraktionen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.400", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie jetzt Wort halten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.240", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die jetzige Situation ist f\u00fcr keine Seite befriedigend. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.120", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der BGH sieht sich mit einer trotz Wertgrenze steigenden Zahl von Nichtzulassungsbeschwerden \u00fcberfordert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.320", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch unabh\u00e4ngig von der Wertgrenze frustriert die mangelnde Voraussehbarkeit der aus BGH-Sicht bestehenden oder fehlenden Revisionsw\u00fcrdigkeit bei einer Zulassungsquote von unter 10\u00a0Prozent nicht nur die Anwaltskollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.440", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern erst recht die Parteien, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.760", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die das finanzielle Risiko tragen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.040", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Effektivierung ging zuweilen zulasten der Akzeptanz h\u00f6chstrichterlicher Rechtsprechung in der Bev\u00f6lkerung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.320", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schaffen wir nun eine transparente und zukunftsweisende Regelung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.960", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "H\u00f6ren wir auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.280", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rechtsuchende mit einer Dauer\u00fcbergangsregelung in die Irre zu f\u00fchren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.200", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verstecken wir k\u00fcnftig die Regelungen nicht mehr im EGZPO. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.360", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie uns dar\u00fcber nachdenken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.400", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob die richtige Reaktion auf steigende Fallzahlen in h\u00f6heren Instanzen aufgrund mangelnder Akzeptanz von Rechtsprechung immer Rechtswegverk\u00fcrzung sein muss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.840", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "M\u00fcssen wir den BGH st\u00e4rker aufstellen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.880", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Brauchen wir eine Reform der Regelung der Statthaftigkeit von Revisionen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.120", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Zulassungsgr\u00fcnde insgesamt? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.360", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nutzen wir die Zeit bis Ende\u00a02019 jetzt wirklich f\u00fcr ein Update."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.000", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der n\u00e4chste Redner ist f\u00fcr die Fraktion Die Linke der Kollege Friedrich Straetmanns."
   ]
  }
 ]
}